short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make all links pass through Google Cache

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When activated, all links on the web page will be automatically modified to pass through Google Cache.
This saves you from needing to search for the cached version on Google.
